title: 4 Delicious and Surprising Blender Recipes
description:
Who knew? Your blender can make so much more than smoothies! Panasonic & Good Housekeeping present: 4 Delicious and Surprising Blender Recipes

Blender Recipe #1) Grind your favorite coffee beans for the perfect pour-over coffee
Blender Recipe #2) Blend tomatoes, basil and seasonings for fresh tomato sauce
Blender Recipe #3) Make homemade whipped cream in seconds
Blender Recipe #4) Create a creamy pesto sauce with your blender and fresh basil
